# Contributing to NariBot

First off, thank you for considering contributing to NariBot! It is people like you who help build tools that actually reach the next billion.

## 🤝 How to Get Involved

### 1. Report Bugs
If you find a technical glitch in our USSD logic or AI response patterns, please open an "Issue" in this repository.

### 2. Suggest Improvements
Have an idea for a better vernacular prompt or a more efficient channel adapter? We want to hear it.

### 3. Documentation
Helping us improve the technical wiki or translate documentation into regional languages is one of the most impactful ways to contribute.

## 📜 Code of Conduct
We are committed to a welcoming and inclusive environment for all contributors, regardless of background or technical skill level.

## ⚖️ License
By contributing, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under the Apache License 2.0.
